# Red Team Tradecraft: Privilege Escalation and Persistence for Defensive Training

## Introduction

This post covers two foundational techniques for Linux post-exploitation: privilege escalation via CVE-2021-4034 (PwnKit) and persistence through a cron-based reverse shell. These are intended for authorized red team exercises and defensive training labs. We'll walk through the exact commands, compilation steps, and logic behind each technique.

